### ============================================================
### SETUP PHASE 1 - Create companies and employees
### Codes are known ahead of time so no dynamic IDs needed yet
### ============================================================

# @name CreateMainCompany
POST {{host}}/api/companies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "TestCorp s.r.o.",
  "companyCode": "CORP-TEST-AUTO",
  "directorId": null
}

###

